{%- comment -%}
  Floating chrome & modals — ported from app.js overlaysHTML().
  WhatsApp float, AI "Find My Scent" concierge, referral modal, Mix-into-Spray wizard.
  All wired by app.js (openAI/closeAI/aiSend/openReferral/closeMix/waChat).
{%- endcomment -%}

